{"tid":1797372,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"一早就開始宣傳先，元旦果日民陣搞大遊行，大家應承我，大家都會入維園出發！！！","createTime":"2019-12-25T10:57:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T04:32:41.000Z","uid":1477,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"3c377336f3a8af587523d988ac1ef3cd76fcd968","tid":1797372,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T10:57:31.000Z","msg":"如果驚塞到痴線，咪遲少少出門口<br />\n記住如果個個都銅鑼灣，灣仔打尖<br />\n咁維園嘅手足就會一直都出唔到發<br />\n最早到嘅佢地，會最遲先到終點<br />\n你忍心手足要企成日咩？<br />\n<br />\n所以，1月1號要出黎<br />\n更加要入維園。<br />\n1月1，維園見。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OwPAWzz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOwPAWzz.jpg&h=ad7c4802&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e0763fe15ca258a5b7745e5c0f95539a170e45a0","tid":1797372,"uid":52090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T10:58:05.000Z","msg":"天后入，銅鑼灣出是常識吧"},{"pid":"be0639aa7e80d56539b6e1db5a72ec8acdf0c383","tid":1797372,"uid":146285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T10:58:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"395b98fb80bb9af7577cda0ce3437b82c8f3073e","tid":1797372,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0763fe15ca258a5b7745e5c0f95539a170e45a0","tid":1797372,"uid":52090,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T10:58:05.000Z","msg":"天后入，銅鑼灣出是常識吧"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:01:42.000Z","msg":"一早宣傳定呢個concept!!!!!<br />\n廢時手足唔知！！"},{"pid":"75d3fb88920b246ff614556b2de9b501ddffc613","tid":1797372,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:02:29.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"cb624ab9ca0b366e77436559c2dec5dec6cf450c","tid":1797372,"uid":156474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:02:39.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"a674172ca960503aa7581ec0d9a51bad31581d9c","tid":1797372,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-25T11:03: